    {
      "id": "2c9e9f9b-4b9d-4883-b6a6-62a5d781b301",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Results show that predictions can be made when only on-third of the course has passed. Moreover, the authors identify critical factors that affect student performance - 4 online and 3 more traditional ones. Combining data from both contexts improves model performance.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
